<p>Function call in For loop condition</p>
<p>Function call inside a for loop condition should not be used:</p>
<ul><li>Example: </li>
    <li>Replace </li>
    <li>for($i = 0; $i < count($array); $i++)</li>
    <li>with $count = count($array); </li>
    <li>for($i = 0; $i < $count; $i++) </li>
</ul>